episodes.title: The Crocodile's Dilemma
episodes.plot: A ruthless, manipulative man meets a small-town insurance salesman and sets him on a path of destruction.

episodes.title: The Rooster Prince
episodes.plot: Molly begins to suspect that Lester is involved in the murders, but her boss points her in a different direction. Meanwhile, Malvo investigates the plot against a man known as the Supermarket King.

episodes.title: A Muddy Road
episodes.plot: Malvo flips the script on the blackmail operation. Molly sets a trap, and Gus debates whether he should come clean. Lester's return to work has complicated repercussions.

episodes.title: Eating the Blame
episodes.plot: When Gus tries to right a wrong, Malvo embraces his alter ego. Lester finds himself in a surprising situation, and Molly uncovers a promising lead.

episodes.title: The Six Ungraspables
episodes.plot: When Lester has a close call, Molly makes an unorthodox decision. Gus weighs some neighborly advice, and Malvo gets what he wants.

episodes.title: Buridan's Ass
episodes.plot: Malvo executes his master plan, while Lester attempts to craft one of his own. Gus and Molly team up in Duluth.

episodes.title: Who Shaves the Barber?
episodes.plot: Molly recuperates from her injury, while Malvo looks to dispatch a syndicate in Fargo. Lester continues his descent into darkness with the unfolding of his plan.

episodes.title: The Heap
episodes.plot: Molly faces pressure to close the case, while Lester starts to feel like a new man.

episodes.title: A Fox, a Rabbit, and a Cabbage
episodes.plot: Lester has an unexpected encounter, Malvo changes course, and a new investigation leads Molly down a familiar path.

episodes.title: Morton's Fork
episodes.plot: Molly takes the lead, while Gus pursues a hunch. Lester manipulates a situation, and Malvo finds a new target.
